Package: cvir
Title: Content Validity Index (CVI) Calculation Tools
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Jesica", "Formoso", , "jesica.formoso@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-3062-4036"))
Description: Provides functions to calculate the Content Validity Index (CVI) for individual items and entire scales based on expert ratings. Includes both item-level CVI calculations and scale-level indices using average and universal agreement methods. Useful for evaluating the content validity of assessment instruments in educational, psychological, or health research.Based on Yusoff (2019), https://doi.org/10.21315/eimj2019.11.2.6
